@node BADLA "Badlands"

@{b}Badlands@{ub}

Rarity  = A/B/UL(R) / RV(R)
Type    = Land
Artist  = Rob Alexander

Text(RV): <T>: Add either <R> or <B> to your mana pool. Counts as both
          mountains and swamp and is affected by spells that affect either.
          If a spell destroys one of these land types, this card is
          destroyed; if a spell alters one of these land types, the other
          land type is unaffected.

Text(UL): Counts as both mountains and swamp and is affected by spells that
          affect either. Tap to add either <R> or <B> to your mana pool.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_B.guide/BADLA}

@endnode
